  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to identify the orofacial difficulties during the maternal
      breastfeeding in rooming-in.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Cross-sectional and quantitative study with sample consisted of 28 dyad present in rooming-in
      of the Assis Chateaubriand School Motherhood during August and December of 2009.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
